{"lastModified":1773084549313,"uri":"c::20370734480::vessel::d5cbab3e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Gulet"],"description":"Operating Area: Greek Islands – Dodecanese, Saronic Islands, Ionian Sea, Mediterranean\n\nVAY is a stunning 40.40-meter luxury motor sailer, built by Su Marine in 2013 and designed by Taka Yachts. With her sleek design and spacious deck, she offers an elegant yet comfortable yachting experience for up to 10 guests. The yacht features 5 beautifully appointed cabins:\n\n1 Master Suite with a king-size bed and en-suite bathroom.\n2 VIP Cabins, each with queen-size beds and en-suite facilities.\n2 Guest Cabins with twin beds, ideal for children or additional guests, both with en-suite bathrooms.\nVAY is perfect for both relaxation and adventure, with a wide range of watersports equipment, including:\n\n2x Ringo inflatables for fun on the water.\n1x Seabob for thrilling underwater exploration.\n2x Paddleboards for serene paddling around the bays.\n1x Wakeboard for those who enjoy adrenaline-pumping activities.\nWater Skis for both adults and children, ensuring everyone can enjoy the fun.\nTenders: A 5m tender with a 70HP engine for transfers, and a powerful 10m Salpa Soleil tender equipped with twin 300HP engines for fast cruising and watersports.\nVAY combines traditional sailing with modern luxury, making it the perfect choice for an unforgettable Greek island adventure.","blueprint":{"name":"VAY","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbab3e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::4b8a8740-9dfa-11f0-92f9-f78c3cb8e879/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbab3e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::4ba7ac31-9dfa-11f0-92f9-f78c3cb8e879/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbab3e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::4b9b2910-9dfa-11f0-92f9-f78c3cb8e879/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbab3e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::4b99c980-9dfa-11f0-b541-33a57185f5ac/{imageVariant}",